short_description: On Tower Road.
description: |
  The dirt road climbs gently into the hills, or descends gently
  towards the forest floor depending on how you look at it. Deep
  ruts in the road have filled with water. The croaking of frogs
  can be heard as you approach each pond, and then the sudden plop!
  plop! plop! of peepers hopping for safety.
